Dialogue: 4,0:23:38.78,0:23:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Risa-chan?
Dialogue: 4,0:23:41.37,0:23:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Deejishichyun saa!
Dialogue: 4,0:23:45.20,0:23:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something they say in Okinawa, where I used to live.
Dialogue: 4,0:23:48.02,0:23:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to say it to you.
