Dialogue: 4,0:23:52.79,0:23:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's embarrassing, so I'm keeping it a secret.
Dialogue: 4,0:23:55.33,0:23:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you someday.
Dialogue: 4,0:23:58.66,0:24:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll get going for real now.
